                </a></li></ul></div><p><strong>Figure 2.  <span>The effectiveness of single-step contact tracing without tracing delays.</span></strong></p><a id="article1.body1.sec3.sec1.fig1.caption1.p1" name="article1.body1.sec3.sec1.fig1.caption1.p1"></a><p>Effectiveness is expressed as the minimum proportion of contacts that need to be traced for effective control (critical tracing probability <em>p<sub>c</sub>
