<a id="article1.body1.sec3.sec1.fig1.caption1.p5" name="article1.body1.sec3.sec1.fig1.caption1.p5"></a><p>Indicated by dashed lines are the average τ<sub>lat</sub> for four infections, in the panels with closest correspondence to the actual parameter values (<a href="#pone-0000012-t002">Table 2</a>).</p>
